"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[![Barack Obama](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*AwBz4NW9\\\\_M45J-sBlmH-lA.png)](https://barackobama.medium.com/?source=post_page-----c54927e7c7cc-----------------------------------)\\n\\n[](https://barackobama.medium.com/?source=post_page-----c54927e7c7cc-----------------------------------)\\n\\n[Barack Obama](https://barackobama.medium.com/?source=post_page-----c54927e7c7cc-----------------------------------)\\n\\n[](https://barackobama.medium.com/my-statement-on-the-passing-of-archbishop-desmond-tutu-c54927e7c7cc?source=post_page-----c54927e7c7cc-----------------------------------)\\n\\n[Â·Dec 26, 2021](https://barackobama.medium.com/my-statement-on-the-passing-of-archbishop-desmond-tutu-c54927e7c7cc?source=post_page-----c54927e7c7cc-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/2000/1\\\\*shS96SZq73sghYMhVZMH2A.jpeg)\\n\\nPhoto by Pete Souza\\n\\nArchbishop Desmond Tutu was a mentor, a friend, and a moral compass for me and so many others. A universal spirit, Archbishop Tutu was grounded in the struggle for liberation and justice in his own country, but also concerned with injustice everywhere. He never lost his impish sense of humor and willingness to find humanity in his adversaries, and Michelle and I will miss him dearly.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641601371,\"title\":\"My Statement on the Passing of Archbishop Desmond Tutu\"},\"digest\":\"zRc9e2xKVD9Ipg5_FdfkuF5jUjAlvL59SbVjK6Lx-V8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x6E8DbDFac46C7d7E3A7e3154Bfe342E41420C3D5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"G7j8Psv-DsYm2xzY-nI47JtPmTtVRqa1t5zqCDwt2Ms\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3Dw_SU6rFKnRKHOO7n1i3rMQi4PvDNkWVbwj8wdOzLQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"wWytGG7UfmGH709D2IUOTAmAGF6XUMtMyvJwwONpJS_8mOyaJBZvzSU5kg_Cg-3zUQc9xNRLCuznfPiAIdy8qw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x520e52e7c206c9c6931cb3d65ec4f11abd010084301f12db6ff8499e1a21adcb25846e3